videos.description: A leak in the ceiling in Toronto caused a short delay to the tip in Game 1 between the Wizards and Raptors.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Wizards-Raptors delayed due to leak from ceiling) 2018/04/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wizards-Raptors delayed due to leak from ceiling

videos.description: Jonas Valanciunas takes Marcin Gortat one-on-one in the post and powers in for the tough layup.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Valanciunas goes to work in the post early) 2018/04/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Valanciunas goes to work in the post early

videos.description: OG Anunoby drills two 3-pointers as Toronto takes control in the 1st quarter vs. Washington.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Anunoby provides 1st-quarter spark for Raptors) 2018/04/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Anunoby provides 1st-quarter spark for Raptors

videos.description: John Wall drives to the rim and finishes through contact for an and-1 in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Wall slices through Raptors for tough and-1

videos.description: Marcin Gortat gets called for a foul as he gets tangled up with Jonas Valanciunas after getting blocked at the rim.
videos.headline: Valanciunas rejects Gortat

videos.description: Kyle Lowry pushes the tempo and hits a 3-pointer as Toronto starts the 3rd quarter on fire.
videos.headline: Lowry drills transition 3

videos.description: Kelly Oubre Jr. hustles to save the ball at all costs, in this case costing Serge Ibaka some pain in the midsection.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Oubre Jr. saves ball, hitting Ibaka below the belt) 2018/04/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Oubre Jr. saves ball, hitting Ibaka below the belt

videos.description: Delon Wright hits a reverse layup and CJ Miles follows it with a 3-pointer as Toronto takes the lead in the 4th quarter.

videos.headline: Drake's hyped after Toronto's 5-0 run

videos.description: After a Game 1 victory, Kyle Lowry wants the Raptors to continue to build off of their strong performance against the Wizards.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (Lowry on win: 'This is the start of something') 2018/04/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lowry on win: 'This is the start of something'

videos.description: DeMar DeRozan explains why the Raptors took Game 1 'as they should' have and how playing at home was a big advantage.

videos.headline: DeRozan on game 1 victory: 'It's out of the way'

videos.description: In a Game 7 atmosphere, the Raptors use efficient shooting from deep and clutch bench play to capture their first ever playoff-opener win.
